sellerCard.description: Web & Software Designer specializing in Framer/Webflow development with a flair for animation and AI-driven illustration creation. My comprehensive skill set covers everything from copywriting to design and development. Hire me if you're looking for innovation at every step of your project.

description.content:
Need a professional Webflow site built from your existing design? Youre in the right place! This gig focuses on Webflow development only turning your approved mockups into a fast, responsive, and user-friendly website. If you need a brand-new design, I offer it separately.


Whats Included

  • Responsive Build: Pixel-perfect execution for desktop, tablet, and mobile.
  • Daily Updates: Check progress every 24 hours and provide feedback.
  • Animations: Smooth transitions and effects to enhance user experience.
  • Blog CMS Setup: Easily manage posts, articles, or product listings.
  • Content Upload: Ill place your images, text, and other media directly in Webflow.
  • Post-Launch Support: One week of minor tweaks or fixes after delivery.


Key Benefits

  • Clear Communication: Im always available for questions or revisions.
  • Scalable Structure: Organized classes and components for future updates.
  • Fast Turnaround: Typical delivery in 1-2 weeks, depending on scope.


Have more than 5 pages or need extra features?

Just add Extra Pages or message me for a custom quote. Lets bring your design to life on Webflow quickly and professionally!

packageList.title: 1 Page Kickstart (Dev Only)
packageList.description: 1-page dev from your design. Responsive, forms, animations. Fast turnaround.

packageList.title: 2 Pages Growth (Dev Only)
packageList.description: 2-page dev from your design. Responsive, content upload, blog CMS, animations included.

packageList.title: Up to 5 Pages Pro (Dev Only)
packageList.description: Development of up to 5 pages. Advanced animations, blog CMS, content upload, 1-week support.
